  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Ferenczy, ?] because somebody said-- one of us said to us that, have a look.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This, this must be [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Ferenczy, ?] because he had a lot of gold in here and a lot of gold in there and bigger feather than the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He, he seems like the, the head man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And after the war, when I came back, we had a connection with the-- with the Hungarian authorities after the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I, I was present of the hanging and the-- and the legal proceedings when these war criminals was brought to justice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I seen that guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was on his [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] trial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they said his name was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Ferenczy. ?] So he was the guy who gave our troop into the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because from then-- until then, the Gendarmes, these people were guarding us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because wherever we stopped, we heard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't open the wagon, but we heard Hungarian talking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "After we left [INAUDIBLE], we heard only German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we knew that we had been taken over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
